%% Diagram: Hybrid recurrence storage — master row + materialized window + on-demand expansion
%% Type: flowchart
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
flowchart LR
    Master["events row<br/>RRULE + DTSTART;TZID<br/>EXDATE / RDATE"]

    subgraph Window["Materialized window (rolling 90d)"]
        I1["instance n"]
        I2["instance n+1"]
        I3["instance n+2"]
        Iex["exception<br/>recurringEventId<br/>originalStartTime"]
    end

    subgraph Future["Beyond window"]
        Lazy["expand on read<br/>RRULE.between(t1, t2)"]
    end

    Past["Past instances<br/>aged out / archived"]

    Master -->|nightly job<br/>materialize next 90d| Window
    Master -->|client query > 90d| Lazy
    Window -->|aged > 90d| Past
    Iex -->|merged at read time| I2

    Reader(["Calendar view query"]) --> Window
    Reader --> Lazy
